<li>Words cannot express the sadness I feel for your family's loss.  Your brother will be deeply missed.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and love as you navigate this difficult journey.</li>
<li>Please accept my heartfelt sympathy on the passing of your beloved brother.</li>
<li>May the love and memories you shared with your brother bring you some comfort.</li>
<li>I am here for you and your family, whatever you need.</li>
<li>Holding you close in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and your family during this time of sorrow.  May his soul rest in peace.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy, I offer my condolences on your brother's passing.</li>
<li>Your brother's memory will live on in the hearts of those who loved him.</li>
<li>May his spirit find eternal peace.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and comfort as you mourn the loss of your brother.</li>
<li>Please know that you are not alone in your grief.</li>
<li>We are sending our love and support to you and your family.</li>
    

